> ⚠️ The last two conditions only match if the INPUT happens to equal the Soundex code. For proper phonetic search in PA, use the **C# plugin approach** (AdvancedPersonSearchPlugin already handles this correctly). That's why we still recommend the Custom API + C# plugin for best AC3 coverage.

**For the PA search flow, the full filter expression:**

